dcterms:description: A statistical distribution that describes the probability of the eigenvalues of random matrices, used as a comparison for quantum distributions.
dcterms:title: Porter-Thomas Distribution

dcterms:description: A derived distribution from the Porter-Thomas distribution that incorporates subset parity ordering.
dcterms:title: Subset Parity Ordered Porter-Thomas Distribution

dcterms:description: A derived distribution from the Porter-Thomas distribution that incorporates random permutation.
dcterms:title: Random Permutation Porter-Thomas Distribution

dcterms:title: Experimental Samples from Quantum Circuits

dcterms:title: Theoretical Quantum Samples

dcterms:title: Classical Distributions for Comparison
